1.0.name: wordpress/redirector
1.0.description:
With this Plugin you can redirect a page in your WordPress installation to any other URL, to a page in your WordPress installation, to the first child page or to https.

!!! WARNING !!! If you update to version 2.0 via auto update, please deactivate the plugin and reactivate it, else your redirections won't work. Sorry for all the hassle!
